{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"C\n    \n      Both: Scaffold + Smart Loading Fallback\n      Best of both worlds. Pre-scaffold the Next.js app in the Docker image so the dev server starts in ~3s. But also have a smart loading overlay that only shows briefly and disappears once the iframe actually loads. If anything goes wrong, the loading screen handles it gracefully.\n      \n        \n          T+0s\n          Brief loading\n          \"Preparing...\"\n        \n        →\n        \n          T+3s\n          Template ready\n          Preview: Default page\n        \n        →\n        \n          T+5s+\n          AI editing\n          Preview: Live updates\n        \n      \n      \n        ProsFastest possible previewGraceful fallbackReal-time AI progress visible\n        ConsMore work (template + loading)","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1773615584722}
